00:02:29.925 --> 00:02:31.250
...akan mati.

00:02:39.620 --> 00:02:40.816
Ayo.  - Ayo.

00:02:41.270 --> 00:02:42.890
Ayo!  - Ayo pergi!

00:02:57.835 --> 00:02:59.624
Apa yang sedang kamu lakukan?

00:03:06.377 --> 00:03:08.781
'Ke mana penduduk
desa membawa Kumud?'

